{"tid":1628653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"團結、團結，再團結，我哋就會贏！","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:15:10.000Z","uid":12661,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e51b5fb8600b54e922af3eae92f05ef69249d114","tid":1628653,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"支共、港共、黑警嘅所作所為有幾離譜、幾過份，已經多到唔駛我講&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋唔滿意政府嘅人多，有唔同聲音，完全正常！我哋要沉着應戰，唔好自亂陣腳&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n明白有和理非有擔心，亦有人怕黑警設局拉人&hellip;只要我哋團結，二百萬、三百萬人，佢哋唔通要拉晒？總之我哋對敵人嘅敵意繼續，我哋咩都唔怕！<br />\n<br />\nBe water ！兄弟爬山、各自努力！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"4bd542d1eb819d6a0e819f91f5c3c016411d519e","tid":1628653,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52608dae974e4f88a5e5ec5c3e5700d673c6458e","tid":1628653,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:06:24.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」都用緊急法立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they have passed the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=ace6466a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"419b3d284548cbafc8ea6e6f4a5b589d986f05b2","tid":1628653,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"127987ea31d26fa1a18fd3c827b0453d36ae3d50","tid":